headline: AbbVie’s (NYSE:ABBV) Q2: Beats On Revenue
summary: Pharmaceutical company AbbVie (NYSE:ABBV) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 6.6% year on year to $15.42 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.97 per share was 2.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: UBS Shrugs Abbott Laboratories’ (ABT) Diagnostic Weakness Affirms ‘Buy’ Rating
summary: Abbott Laboratories (NYSE:ABT) is one of the defensive stocks that billionaires are buying amid US trade tariff uncertainty. On July 21, UBS reiterated a ‘Buy’ rating and a $148 price target on the stock. The bullish stance comes on the heels of the stock coming under pressure following the release of lower fiscal year 2025 […]
